title: Ravens rally late, top Steelers 23-20 in overtime (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 53,993 Ravens rally late, top Steelers 23-20 in overtime (Yahoo Sports) The big-legged Baltimore kicker hit a 42-yard field goal to tie the Pittsburgh Steelers in the final seconds of regulation and made a 52-yarder with 5:08 left in overtime to give the Ravens a 23-20 victory Thursday night. Scobee had two chances to give the Steelers some cushion late in the fourth quarter only to pull both kicks wide left. The second miss gave the Ravens (1-3) enough time to put Scobee well within range to send the game to an extra period.
